'''luff'''[[Category:English nouns that lack inflection template]]

# {{nautical}} The [[vertical]] [[edge]] of a [[sail]] that is closest to the direction of the [[wind]].
#:'''By easing the [[halyard]] the '''luff''' of the sail sagged to [[leeward]].''

